<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Candy Crush Game Development Prompt</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #f5576c;
            margin-top: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #f093fb;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.8em;
        }

        h3 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 1.3em;
        }

        h4 {
            color: #764ba2;
            margin-top: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        ul, ol {
            margin-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        strong {
            color: #f5576c;
        }

        .level-section {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 5px solid #f093fb;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .level-section h4 {
            color: #f5576c;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .grid-item {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 3px solid #667eea;
        }

        .grid-item strong {
            display: block;
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .tech-stack {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .tech-item {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-top: 4px solid #667eea;
        }

        .tech-item strong {
            display: block;
            color: #f5576c;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }

        .difficulty-levels {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .difficulty-card {
            background: white;
            border: 2px solid #667eea;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .difficulty-card:hover {
            box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .difficulty-card h4 {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            margin: -20px -20px 15px -20px;
            border-radius: 6px 6px 0 0;
        }

        .difficulty-info {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 0.95em;
        }

        .difficulty-info p {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .difficulty-info strong {
            color: #f5576c;
        }

        .table-responsive {
            overflow-x: auto;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            background: white;
        }

        table th {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        table td {
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        table tr:hover {
            background: #f8f9fa;
        }

        .section-divider {
            margin: 40px 0;
            border: 0;
            border-top: 3px dashed #667eea;
        }

        .highlight {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .success-metrics {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 10px;
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        .metric {
            background: #d4edda;
            border-left: 4px solid #28a745;
            padding: 12px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .metric::before {
            content: "✓ ";
            color: #28a745;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .grid, .tech-stack, .difficulty-info, .success-metrics {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .header h1 {
                font-size: 1.8em;
            }

            h2 {
                font-size: 1.4em;
            }

            .content {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }

        .footer {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .toc {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 2px solid #667eea;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .toc h3 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .toc ul {
            columns: 2;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .toc li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .toc a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .toc a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
            color: #f5576c;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🍬 Candy Crush Game Development Prompt</h1>
            <p>A Comprehensive Guide for Building a Match-3 Puzzle Game with 10 Progressive Difficulty Levels</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <!-- Table of Contents -->
            <div class="toc">
                <h3>📋 Quick Navigation</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#overview">Project Overview</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#features">Game Features</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#difficulty">Difficulty Levels</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#systems">Game Systems</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#technical">Technical Requirements</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#metrics">Success Metrics</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <!-- Project Overview -->
            <section id="overview">
                <h2>📌 Project Overview</h2>
                <p>Develop a fully functional Candy Crush-style puzzle game with progressive difficulty levels (1-10) and engaging gameplay mechanics.</p>
                <div class="highlight">
                    <strong>Goal:</strong> Create an addictive, well-balanced match-3 puzzle game that retains players through carefully designed difficulty progression and rewarding gameplay mechanics.
                </div>
            </section>

            <hr class="section-divider">

            <!-- Game Core Features -->
            <section id="features">
                <h2>🎮 Game Core Features</h2>

                <h3>1. Game Mechanics</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Match-3 System:</strong> Players swap adjacent candies to create matches of 3 or more identical candies</li>
                    <li><strong>Board Grid:</strong> 8x8 game board with various candy types</li>
                    <li><strong>Gravity System:</strong> Candies fall downward after matches are cleared</li>
                    <li><strong>Cascading Matches:</strong> Automatic chain reactions when new candies form matches after falling</li>
                    <li><strong>Special Candies:</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Striped Candy: Clears entire row/column</li>
                            <li>Wrapped Candy: Clears 3x3 area</li>
                            <li>Color Bomb: Eliminates all candies of one color</li>
                            <li>Ingredients: Must be collected and moved to the bottom</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h3>2. Game Modes</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Classic Mode:</strong> Reach a target score within limited moves</li>
                    <li><strong>Timed Mode:</strong> Score as many points as possible in 60 seconds</li>
                    <li><strong>Ingredient Mode:</strong> Collect specific ingredients and drop them to the bottom</li>
                    <li><strong>Moves Limited:</strong> Complete objective within a fixed number of moves</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>3. Scoring System</h3>
                <div class="grid">
                    <div class="grid-item">
                        <strong>Basic Match (3 candies):</strong> 10 points
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid-item">
                        <strong>4-Match (striped candy):</strong> 25 points
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid-item">
                        <strong>5-Match (color bomb):</strong> 50 points
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid-item">
                        <strong>Cascades:</strong> 1.2x bonus multiplier per cascade
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid-item">
                        <strong>Time Bonuses:</strong> Extra points for quick completion
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid-item">
                        <strong>Combo Bonus:</strong> 2x, 3x, 4x, 5x (max) for consecutive matches
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <hr class="section-divider">

            <!-- Difficulty Levels -->
            <section id="difficulty">
                <h2>🎯 Difficulty Levels (1-10)</h2>

                <div class="difficulty-card">
                    <h4>Level 1 - Tutorial/Easy</h4>
                    <div class="difficulty-info">
                        <p><strong>Moves:</strong> 40</p>
                        <p><strong>Target Score:</strong> 5,000 points</p>
                        <p><strong>Board Size:</strong> 8x8</p>
                        <p><strong>Obstacles:</strong> None</p>
                        <p><strong>Candy Types:</strong> 4 colors</p>
                        <p><strong>Time Limit:</strong> None</p>
                    </div>
                    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Simple match-3 to learn mechanics</p>
                </div>

                <div class="difficulty-card">
                    <h4>Level 2 - Easy</h4>
                    <div class="difficulty-info">
                        <p><strong>Moves:</strong> 35</p>
                        <p><strong>Target Score:</strong> 8,000 points</p>
                        <p><strong>Obstacles:</strong> 2-3 locked candies</p>
                        <p><strong>Candy Types:</strong> 4 colors</p>
                    </div>
                    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Introduce locked candies mechanic</p>
                </div>

                <div class="difficulty-card">
                    <h4>Level 3 - Easy+</h4>
                    <div class="difficulty-info">
                        <p><strong>Moves:</strong> 30</p>
                        <p><strong>Target Score:</strong> 10,000 points</p>
                        <p><strong>Obstacles:</strong> Locked candies, 1-2 licorice walls</p>
                        <p><strong>Candy Types:</strong> 5 colors</p>
                    </div>
                    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Introduce board obstacles</p>
                </div>

                <div class="difficulty-card">
                    <h4>Level 4 - Medium</h4>
                    <div class="difficulty-info">
                        <p><strong>Moves:</strong> 28</p>
                        <p><strong>Target Score:</strong> 15,000 points</p>
                        <p><strong>Obstacles:</strong> Licorice walls, locked candies, ice blocks</p>
                        <p><strong>Candy Types:</strong> 5 colors</p>
                    </div>
                    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Combine obstacles and new mechanics</p>
                </div>

                <div class="difficulty-card">
                    <h4>Level 5 - Medium</h4>
                    <div class="difficulty-info">
                        <p><strong>Moves:</strong> 25</p>
                        <p><strong>Target Score:</strong> 20,000 points</p>
                        <p><strong>Obstacles:</strong> Ice blocks, licorice walls, 1-2 ingredients</p>
                        <p><strong>Candy Types:</strong> 5 colors</p>
                    </div>
                    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Introduce collection objectives</p>
                </div>

                <div class="difficulty-card">
                    <h4>Level 6 - Medium+</h4>
                    <div class="difficulty-info">
                        <p><strong>Moves:</strong> 22</p>
                        <p><strong>Target Score:</strong> 25,000 points</p>
                        <p><strong>Obstacles:</strong> Ice blocks (3 layers), ingredients, licorice, concrete</p>
                        <p><strong>Candy Types:</strong> 6 colors</p>
                    </div>
                    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Higher complexity with multiple objective types</p>
                </div>

                <div class="difficulty-card">
                    <h4>Level 7 - Hard</h4>
                    <div class="difficulty-info">
                        <p><strong>Moves:</strong> 20</p>
                        <p><strong>Target Score:</strong> 30,000 points</p>
                        <p><strong>Obstacles:</strong> Heavy ice, concrete, licorice, 3-4 ingredients</p>
                        <p><strong>Candy Types:</strong> 6 colors</p>
                    </div>
                    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Requires strategic planning</p>
                </div>

                <div class="difficulty-card">
                    <h4>Level 8 - Hard+</h4>
                    <div class="difficulty-info">
                        <p><strong>Moves:</strong> 18</p>
                        <p><strong>Target Score:</strong> 40,000 points</p>
                        <p><strong>Obstacles:</strong> Ice, concrete, teleporters, 4-5 ingredients</p>
                        <p><strong>Candy Types:</strong> 6 colors</p>
                    </div>
                    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Complex puzzle-solving required</p>
                </div>

                <div class="difficulty-card">
                    <h4>Level 9 - Expert</h4>
                    <div class="difficulty-info">
                        <p><strong>Moves:</strong> 15</p>
                        <p><strong>Target Score:</strong> 50,000 points</p>
                        <p><strong>Obstacles:</strong> All previous + jelly blocks, 5 ingredients</p>
                        <p><strong>Candy Types:</strong> 6 colors</p>
                    </div>
                    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Expert-level challenge</p>
                </div>

                <div class="difficulty-card">
                    <h4>Level 10 - Master</h4>
                    <div class="difficulty-info">
                        <p><strong>Moves:</strong> 12</p>
                        <p><strong>Target Score:</strong> 75,000 points</p>
                        <p><strong>Obstacles:</strong> Extreme density, dynamic regenerating obstacles</p>
                        <p><strong>Candy Types:</strong> 6 colors</p>
                    </div>
                    <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Ultimate challenge requiring optimal play</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <hr class="section-divider">

            <!-- Game Systems -->
            <section id="systems">
                <h2>⚙️ Game Systems</h2>

                <h3>1. User Interface</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Main Menu:</strong> Play, Settings, Achievements, Leaderboard, Shop</li>
                    <li><strong>Level Select:</strong> Display completed levels, stars earned (0-3), best score</li>
                    <li><strong>Game Screen:</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Game board</li>
                            <li>Score display</li>
                            <li>Move counter or timer</li>
                            <li>Objective display</li>
                            <li>Pause button</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Game Over Screen:</strong> Final score, stars earned, next level button, retry button</li>
                    <li><strong>Shop System:</strong> Purchase boosters (extra moves, power-ups, etc.)</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>2. Progression System</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Star Ranking:</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>1 Star: Reach target score</li>
                            <li>2 Stars: Reach 1.3x target score</li>
                            <li>3 Stars: Reach 1.7x target score</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Unlock System:</strong> Levels unlock sequentially; must complete previous level</li>
                    <li><strong>Daily Challenges:</strong> Bonus rewards for playing daily</li>
                    <li><strong>Achievement System:</strong> Badges for milestones</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>3. Boosters & Power-ups</h3>
                <div class="grid">
                    <div>
                        <h4>Pre-Game Boosters (Purchased)</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Extra 5/10 moves</li>
                            <li>Striped candy at start</li>
                            <li>Color bomb at start</li>
                            <li>Pre-filled power-ups</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h4>In-Game Power-ups (Created During Gameplay)</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Striped Candy: Row/column clear</li>
                            <li>Wrapped Candy: 3x3 area clear</li>
                            <li>Color Bomb: All one color elimination</li>
                            <li>Wrapped + Striped: Large area explosion</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h3>4. Persistence & Data</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Save System:</strong> Auto-save progress after each level</li>
                    <li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> Store player stats (levels completed, total score, coins, lives)</li>
                    <li><strong>Leaderboard:</strong> Track best scores per level</li>
                    <li><strong>Backup:</strong> Cloud sync for account recovery</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>5. Animations & Feedback</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Smooth Animations:</strong> Candy swaps, matches, falls, and cascades</li>
                    <li><strong>Visual Feedback:</strong> Particle effects on matches, explosion effects</li>
                    <li><strong>Audio:</strong> Sound effects for matches, level completion, game over</li>
                    <li><strong>Haptic Feedback:</strong> Vibrations on mobile for matches and feedback</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <hr class="section-divider">

            <!-- Technical Requirements -->
            <section id="technical">
                <h2>💻 Technical Requirements</h2>

                <h3>Technology Stack</h3>
                <div class="tech-stack">
                    <div class="tech-item">
                        <strong>Frontend</strong>
                        JavaScript/TypeScript, HTML5 Canvas or WebGL for rendering
                    </div>
                    <div class="tech-item">
                        <strong>Framework</strong>
                        React, Vue, or vanilla JS with optimized rendering
                    </div>
                    <div class="tech-item">
                        <strong>Backend</strong>
                        Node.js/Express for leaderboard and cloud saves
                    </div>
                    <div class="tech-item">
                        <strong>Database</strong>
                        MongoDB or Firebase for user data
                    </div>
                    <div class="tech-item">
                        <strong>Mobile</strong>
                        React Native or Flutter for iOS/Android
                    </div>
                </div>

                <h3>Performance Requirements</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>FPS:</strong> Maintain 60 FPS minimum</li>
                    <li><strong>Memory:</strong> Optimize for low-memory devices</li>
                    <li><strong>Network:</strong> Minimal bandwidth usage for saves/leaderboard sync</li>
                    <li><strong>Offline Mode:</strong> Game playable without internet connection</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Browser Compatibility</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Chrome (latest 2 versions)</li>
                    <li>Firefox (latest 2 versions)</li>
                    <li>Safari (latest 2 versions)</li>
                    <li>Mobile browsers (iOS Safari, Chrome Mobile)</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <hr class="section-divider">

            <!-- Success Metrics -->
            <section id="metrics">
                <h2>📊 Success Metrics</h2>
                <div class="success-metrics">
                    <div class="metric">All 10 levels playable and balanced</div>
                    <div class="metric">60 FPS performance on target devices</div>
                    <div class="metric">Average level completion time: 2-5 minutes</div>
                    <div class="metric">Difficulty curve properly calibrated</div>
                    <div class="metric">95%+ user retention after level 1</div>
                    <div class="metric">70%+ players reach level 5+</div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <hr class="section-divider">

            <!-- Development Phases -->
            <section>
                <h2>📅 Development Roadmap</h2>
                <div class="grid">
                    <div class="grid-item">
                        <strong>Phase 1: Core Foundation (Weeks 1-2)</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Set up project structure</li>
                            <li>Implement basic 8x8 board</li>
                            <li>Create candy objects and rendering</li>
                            <li>Implement swap mechanic</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid-item">
                        <strong>Phase 2: Game Mechanics (Weeks 3-4)</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Match detection (3+ candies)</li>
                            <li>Gravity/falling system</li>
                            <li>Cascading matches</li>
                            <li>Score calculation</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid-item">
                        <strong>Phase 3: Obstacles & Special Candies (Weeks 5-6)</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Obstacle types implementation</li>
                            <li>Special candy generation</li>
                            <li>Power mechanics</li>
                            <li>Test combinations</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid-item">
                        <strong>Phase 4: Difficulty System (Weeks 7-8)</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Design 10 difficulty levels</li>
                            <li>Balance and progression</li>
                            <li>Level data configuration</li>
                            <li>Difficulty curve testing</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid-item">
                        <strong>Phase 5: UI & Polish (Weeks 9-10)</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Menu system development</li>
                            <li>Game screens and overlays</li>
                            <li>Animations and effects</li>
                            <li>Sound effects</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid-item">
                        <strong>Phase 6: Testing & Optimization (Weeks 11-12)</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Performance optimization</li>
                            <li>Bug fixes and balancing</li>
                            <li>User testing</li>
                            <li>Final polish</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Future Expansion -->
            <section>
                <h2>🚀 Future Expansion Features</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Multiplayer/PvP mode</li>
                    <li>Seasonal events and special levels</li>
                    <li>Character customization</li>
                    <li>Daily and weekly missions</li>
                    <li>Social features (invite friends, gift lives)</li>
                    <li>Video ads for rewards</li>
                    <li>In-app purchases integration</li>
                    <li>Analytics and heatmaps for balancing</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>🍬 Candy Crush Game Development Prompt - Created for Game Development Teams</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 0.9em;">Last Updated: 2026 | Version 1.0</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>